441
00:29:37,295 --> 00:29:38,305
Kenapa kau datang?

442
00:29:39,324 --> 00:29:40,849
Kau punya hal untuk dikatakan.

443
00:29:43,134 --> 00:29:45,256
Malam terakhir sebelum Ji Eun meninggal...

