00:54:44,631 --> 00:54:45,773
Perasaanku?

769
00:54:47,862 --> 00:54:48,942
Iya.

770
00:54:52,302 --> 00:54:53,383
Kau gila?

771
00:54:53,901 --> 00:54:56,264
Kenapa aku harus menikahimu 
