773
00:55:10,822 --> 00:55:13,084
Lalu bisakah kita berteman saja?

774
00:55:18,201 --> 00:55:19,374
"Teman"?

775
00:55:20,461 --> 00:55:21,512
Iya.

776
00:55:24,842 --> 00:55:25,952
Teman.

777
00:55:27,401 --> 00:55:28,451
Aku hanya...

778
00:55:32,042 --> 00:55:34,032
